'''Chubar''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0686><U+0648><U+0628><U+0631>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''Ch<U+016B>bar''', '''Choobor''', '''Chowbar''', and '''Chuber'''; also known as '''Chobar''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3058821|Chubar}}</ref> is a village in [[Chubar Rural District (Shaft County)|Chubar Rural District]], [[Ahmadsargurab District]], [[Shaft County]], [[Gilan Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 1,248, in 335 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|01}}</ref>  

